      "writtenOn": "2020-07-14T19:19:27Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I\u0027m curious why we don\u0027t use SkTQSort() for these also, leaving the algorithm choice up to that like all the other sorters.",
      "revId": "e6d01aaa81440b832da1a610fb5e68ea2aec70dd",
